  <summary date="2021-02-17T15:03:13Z" status="Introduced in House">Election Fraud Prevention Act

This bill requires each state, in order to receive certain election assistance funds, to prohibit the knowing collection and transmission of a ballot in a federal election that was mailed to another person (commonly referred to as ballot harvesting), with exceptions.</summary>
